  "text": "Psychological counseling should be made available to all patients both for learning pain management coping techniques and for emotional support. EDS often has comorbid anxiety and depression [CITATION_1] . Due to the unrecognized nature of EDS, patients often are made to feel discredited and isolated, and should be offered therapeutic support.",
